<banana>repetends management</banana>
<white>Type param /k to return all available keywords</white>

<lightblue>usage</lightblue> <snow>repetends %action%</snow>

<lightblue>%action%</lightblue> <snow>set | remove | flush | list | suggest</snow>

<lightblue>repetends set a [a*6]</lightblue>
<cadetblue>associate the repetend '[a*6]' to words ending with 'a'</cadetblue>

<lightblue>repetends remove a</lightblue>
<cadetblue>remove the repetend for words ending with 'a'</cadetblue>

<lightblue>repetends flush</lightblue>
<cadetblue>flush the list of repetends away</cadetblue>

<lightblue>repetends list</lightblue>
<cadetblue>show the list of repetends</cadetblue>

<lightblue>repetends suggest n</lightblue>
<cadetblue>compile the list of repetends with length n</cadetblue>

<lightblue>repetends release</lightblue>
<cadetblue>return the latest release date for this command</cadetblue>